deck: Writer and artist with a long history in comics including MISADVENTURES OF ADAM WEST, THE TRAGIC TALE OF TURKEY BOY and DRACULA'S ARMY from McFarland Press.
description:
Andy Fish is a comic book artist and writer, his work has appeared in a variety of books from a long list of publishers.

His latest is DRACULA'S ARMY from McFarland Books which is a follow up to his graphic novel WEREWOLVES OF WISCONSIN published by the same company two years earlier.

Additional credits include FREEKISH BLUES, THE MIS-ADVENTURES OF ADAM WEST, THE TRAGIC TALE OF TURKEY BOY, FLY; A TRUE STORY COMPLETELY MADE UP, ADAM BOMB ADVENTURES, JERRY CLAUS; THE STORY OF DARK SANTA and many more.

Amazon has a page devoted to his work.
name: Andy Fish
